лPeter & Muriel Kenny
We wrote your name In the sand, but the waves washed it away
We wrote your name in the sky, but the clouds blew it away
So we wrote your name in our hearts and forever it will stay"т
яIn loving memory of a very special person
Gioacchino Visaggi who fell asleep on the 30 May 2016
He will be truly missed by his wife and two daughters
whom he dedicated his entire life, and all those who were
helped by his enormous generosity
He has shown to us all to never give up fighting in our
beliefs despite all the hardships"ь
уIn celebration of the marriage of
Dan Moss and Claudie Sellers
18th July 2015
So, she leaning on her husband's arm, they turned homeward
by a rosy path which the gracious sun struck out for them in its setting"ш
